        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Federal Emergency Judicial Tolling Act</b></p> <p>This bill tolls (i.e., pauses) the statute of limitations for criminal and civil actions under federal law during the period of January 31, 2020, through December 31, 2020. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
